♪ I believe, yes ♪

01:35:01.743 --> 01:35:03.745
♪ I say I believe right now ♪

01:35:03.787 --> 01:35:06.039
♪ I believe ♪

01:35:06.331 --> 01:35:08.208
♪ Yes I believe ♪

01:35:08.583 --> 01:35:13.004
♪ Well I believe
to my soul now ♪

01:35:14.339 --> 01:35:16.549
♪ You're tryin' to make
a fool of me ♪

01:35:17.133 --> 01:35:21.054
♪ I believe, yes I believe ♪

01:35:21.137 --> 01:35:22.639
Hold on, wait, wait.

01:35:22.722 --> 01:35:25.016
Cut, cut, cut. You know,
y'all know that sounds off.

01:35:25.100 --> 01:35:27.477
Ahem, you know what,
the three-part harmony is off.

01:35:27.602 --> 01:35:30.396
Let's start it all over again,
uh, from the top with the band.

01:35:31.481 --> 01:35:35.068
♪ I believe it, I believe it ♪

01:35:35.151 --> 01:35:37.320
Whoa, pardner!
Uh, what was that?

01:35:37.570 --> 01:35:40.240
I knew you'd like that, Ray.
It's an eight-track. We just got it.

01:35:40.323 --> 01:35:42.158
We can record each part separately.

01:35:42.242 --> 01:35:44.953
Whoa, Nellie! You know,
I can't wait to see that.

01:35:46.121 --> 01:35:47.705
What's so funny?

01:35:47.789 --> 01:35:49.207
Nothing, "pardner."

01:35:50.750 --> 01:35:52.127
Margie's drunk. Jeff?

01:35:53.920 --> 01:35:55.380
You should go home
and sleep it off.

01:35:55.463 --> 01:35:57.423
Margie, come on now,
let me take you home.

01:35:57.465 --> 01:35:59.551
No! I'll leave when I'm good
and goddamn ready!

01:35:59.634 --> 01:36:01.261
She's good and goddamn
ready right now.

01:36:01.344 --> 01:36:03.596
Why don't you make me
leave this, sucker!

01:36:03.638 --> 01:36:06.099
Teach you to treat me
like some piece of meat!

01:36:06.724 --> 01:36:08.101
I ain't shutting up!

01:36:08.184 --> 01:36:09.853
- Should we get in there?
- No.

01:36:09.936 --> 01:36:11.271
Get them all out, right now.

01:36:11.354 --> 01:36:12.605
You'll have to make me leave!

01:36:12.689 --> 01:36:15.525
You know what, Jeff?
Get all of them out of here.

01:36:15.650 --> 01:36:17.735
You're a cold-ass bastard!

01:36:17.819 --> 01:36:18.987
Let go of me, Jeff!

01:36:19.070 --> 01:36:20.905
You're a cold-ass bastard, Ray!

01:36:20.989 --> 01:36:24.492
See, he wouldn't spit on me
if my ass was on fire!

01:36:24.576 --> 01:36:25.660
Damn right I wouldn't.

01:36:25.743 --> 01:36:27.787
Put me down, Jeff!
Put me down! Damn it!

01:36:28.163 --> 01:36:29.456
You dropped your shoe.

01:36:31.499 --> 01:36:33.877
All right, come on,
let's get back to work.

01:36:33.960 --> 01:36:35.753
Tom, this is
what I want you to do.

01:36:35.837 --> 01:36:38.298
We'll lay my vocals down
and finish the harmony parts.

01:36:38.381 --> 01:36:40.884
Uh, how're we gonna do
the harmonies, Ray?

01:36:40.967 --> 01:36:42.010
You sent the girls home.

01:36:42.093 --> 01:36:44.471
I know what I did with the girls.
Let me take care of that.

01:36:44.512 --> 01:36:47.474
You just turn that eight-track on,
and I'll do the girls' parts myself.

01:36:47.557 --> 01:36:50.477
And go out here somewhere and
find me an "Oh, Johnny" girl.

01:36:50.852 --> 01:36:52.479
Uh, one minute.

01:36:53.480 --> 01:36:55.064
What the hell's an "Oh, Johnny" girl?

01:36:55.190 --> 01:36:56.775
I think I've got an idea.

